text.section:
In this section, "institution" includes:
A hospital;
A nursing home;
A hospice facility;
A medical clinic in a correctional facility;
An inpatient psychiatric facility; and
An inpatient drug rehabilitation facility.

The report shall:
Be on the form that the Secretary provides;
Identify the disease;
State the name, age, race, sex, and residence address of the individual with the disease;
State the name of the administrative head of the institution; and
State the address of the institution.
